(1, 1, '2014-04-29 17:41:22', '2014-04-29 17:41:22', 'In order to successfully read this blog (and succeed at life in general), you need only to know 5 things: I am Ryan, My wife is Alysa, My son is Samuel, My dog is Elanor, We live in Colorado. Now that we got that out of the way, let''s talk design.\r\nI''ve recently had this idea....', '5 Nouns You (yes you) Absolutely MUST Know to Succeed at Life (or this blog)', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'succeed-at-life', '', '', '2014-08-20 14:55:15', '2014-08-20 14:55:15', '', 0, 'http://www.ardesignshop.com/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2, 1, '2014-04-29 17:41:22', '2014-04-29 17:41:22', '<style> p.left, p.right {font-size:20px;line-height:1.4em;font-family:''cabinregular'';}article div h1.home {margin-top:0px!important;}</style>\r\n<h1 class="home">Thoughtful Design & Cutting Edge Web Development </h1>\r\n<p class="left">We cultivate brand identities that deliver the exact narrative from which you''ve built your product or service. We aid your brand in facilitating an easy transition from prospective client to life long customer. When you''ve put in sleepless nights and countless hours to get your service up and running, we only feel it''s fair to give you the same amount of dedication towards your brands identity.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- <a href="https://plus.google.com/116160497239328142248" rel="publisher">Google+</a> <div><a id="id-one" class="home-gallery" href="/colorado-logo-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Logo</span></a><a id="id-two" class="home-gallery" href="/colorado-identity-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Identity</span></a><a id="id-three" class="home-gallery" href="/marketing-materials/"><span class="gallery-home">Marketing</span></a><a id="id-four" class="home-gallery" href="/poster-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Posters</span></a><a id="id-five" class="home-gallery" href="/editorial-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Editorial</span></a><a id="id-six" class="home-gallery" href="/invitation-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Invitations</span></a><a id="id-seven" class="home-gallery" href="/web-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Web Design</span></a><a id="id-eight" class="home-gallery" href="http://www.ardesignshop.com/colorado-logo-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Don''t</span></a><a id="id-nine" class="home-gallery" href="http://www.ardesignshop.com/colorado-logo-design/"><span class="gallery-home">Click</span></a></div> -->', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-04-06 03:47:01', '2015-04-06 03:47:01', '', 0, 'http://www.ardesignshop