(7, 1, '2014-05-01 15:17:05', '2014-05-01 15:17:05', '<h2>Your logo is only the beginning</h2>\r\nWhen it comes to branding your business or idea, it all starts with a logo. Luckily, that is one of the many areas that we shine.\r\n\r\nOur process relies a great deal on what message you want to convey to your client. We don''t simply think of a logo as a stand alone piece of art, but the first step in a much more intentional and structured marketing plan. Your client or customer wants to hold a physical piece of information, and be guided through the important aspects that you choose to highlight.\r\n\r\nWe will start with your logo, but see what other possibilities there are for your marketing materials:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Logo/Brand Development</li>\r\n	<li>Letterhead</li>\r\n	<li>Business Cards</li>\r\n	<li>Envelopes</li>\r\n	<li>Brochures</li>\r\n	<li>Quarterly Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Invitations</li>\r\n	<li>Posters</li>\r\n	<li>Environmental Design</li>\r\n	<li>We could go on forever....</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Some Samples</h3>\r\n\r\n[gallery columns="5" link="file" ids="118,117,116,115,114,113,112,111,106,107,108,109,110,105,104,103,102,101,97,98,99,100" orderby="rand"]', 'Print Design', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'colorado-graphic-design', '', '', '2014-07-27 02:57:54', '2014-07-27 02:57:54', '', 0, 'http://www.ardesignshop.com/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
