(129, 1, '2014-07-27 02:24:24', '2014-07-27 02:24:24', '<h2>As technology improves, we improve with it</h2>\n\nYour website is without a doubt your virtual storefront. Whether you offer a product or a service, your website is a great place to really attract your clientele. Your site is an extension of your identity, your message, and your print advertising. They should all compliment each other, and their message should be consistent.\n\nThere are a number of ways we can build your website, but it all depends on what you want the site to do, and how your visitors should interact with your site. Do you want static content, that sits on your site collecting dust, or do you want robust dynamic content that changes every time a visitor refreshes the page?\n\nThere are a lot of question when it comes to designing and developing a website, and you are the only who can answer those questions. Luckily, we know what the questions are.  Here are some of the ways we can establish your business on the web, and spread your message efficiently and effectively.\n<ul>\n	<li>Website Design</li>\n	<li>Website Development</li>\n	<li>Responsive Design</li>\n	<li>CMS Development (Wordpress/Drupal)</li>\n	<li>Search Engine Optimization</li>\n	<li>Email/Video Marketing</li>\n	<li>Social Media Marketing</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Some Samples</h3>\n[gallery link="file" columns="4" ids="91,92,93,94,95,96"]\n', 'Colorado Web Design & Marketing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-27 02:24:24', '2014-07-27 02:24:24', '', 10, 'http://www.ardesignshop.com/uncategorized/10-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
